  "title": "Yeet",
  "description": "A mod about throwing things.",
  "body": "# Yeet!\n\nYeet is a very simple mod about throwing things.\n\nYeet allows you to hold down the drop key (default Q) to wind up your arm.\nRelease it to throw your items farther.\n\n![Steve holding a diamond, winding up his arm to throw it](https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/steve.png?raw=true)\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/trajectory.png?raw=true\" alt=\"The trajectory of an item after being thrown\" width=\"600\"/>\n\nThrown items can be directly caught by other players.\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/catch_start.png?raw=true\" alt=\"One player winds up their arm to throw an item\" width=\"600\"/>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/catch_mid.png?raw=true\" alt=\"The thrown item is mid-air, flying towards player 2\" width=\"600\"/>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/catch_end.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Player 2 catches the flying item\" width=\"600\"/>\n\nFriend running low on materials? Just throw them some more!\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/TropheusJ/yeet/blob/main/media/materials.png?raw=true\" alt=\"A player throwing some more materials up to their friend\" width=\"600\"/>",
